            <div id="collapseEight" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingEight" data-parent="#accordion">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="shorten">
                        We use state-of-the-art instant foam packaging.
                        Your gift will NEVER arrive with annoying popcorn and will be out of the box in seconds.
                        The foam is perfectly formed to the contents of your gift and will require zero cleanup or hassle.
                        Look for our competitors to use popcorn, paper, bubble wrap and other inferior packaging materials
                        that while they protect the gift in transit, severely hinder the presentation and diminish the enjoyment of receiving the gift.
                    </p>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

